workflow.name: AI-powered client onboarding with Jotform, Asana, Slack, and HubSpot
workflow.description:
Streamline client onboarding and project setup from hours to minutes with AI-driven automation.
This intelligent workflow eliminates manual coordination, builds proposals, creates projects in Asana, welcomes clients on Slack, and logs everything ‚Äî ensuring 90% faster onboarding and zero dropped steps.

## What This Workflow Does

Transforms your client onboarding from scattered tools and emails into one seamless automation:

üìù Capture Client Details ‚Äì Jotform intake form collects client, company, and project information.

üß† AI-Powered Analysis ‚Äì LangChain AI Agent analyzes the project scope, estimates effort, and recommends team composition.

üìÑ Generate Proposal ‚Äì Automatically builds a professional HTML proposal summarizing goals, timeline, and estimated hours.

üóÇÔ∏è Create Asana Project ‚Äì Generates a new project with all key details, milestones, and assigned team members.

üí¨ Slack Collaboration ‚Äì Creates a dedicated Slack channel, sends welcome messages, and introduces the project team.

üìß Welcome Email ‚Äì Sends a personalized onboarding email to the client with project summary and next steps.

üíº CRM Sync ‚Äì Creates or updates a HubSpot contact with complete project and client information.

üìä Audit Logging ‚Äì Logs all onboarding activity to Google Sheets for centralized record-keeping.

## Key Features

ü§ñ AI Proposal Generation ‚Äì Uses LangChain AI to generate smart project summaries and resource plans.

‚öôÔ∏è End-to-End Automation ‚Äì From form submission to project creation, communication, and CRM logging.

üí¨ Smart Slack Setup ‚Äì Automatic channel creation and messaging for internal coordination.

üìß Personalized Client Emails ‚Äì Beautifully formatted, professional onboarding emails.

üóÇÔ∏è Asana Integration ‚Äì Project creation with dynamic task templates and priorities.

üìä Google Sheets Logging ‚Äì Instant audit trail for every client submission and generated proposal.

üíº CRM Integration ‚Äì Automatically syncs client data with HubSpot for sales and account tracking.

## Perfect For

üöÄ Agencies & Service Providers ‚Äì Automate client onboarding, proposal creation, and task setup.

üè¢ Consultancies ‚Äì Quickly turn client requests into structured projects with assigned resources.

üíª Freelancers & Creators ‚Äì Impress clients with AI-built proposals and instant communication.

üìà Growing Teams ‚Äì Scale onboarding without extra admin or coordination time.

üß† Operations Teams ‚Äì Ensure consistency and transparency across all onboarding activities.

## What You‚Äôll Need
### Required Integrations

üßæ Jotform ‚Äì Client intake form (project details, budget, company info).
Create your form for free on [Jotform using this link](https://www.jotform.com/?partner=mediajade)

ü§ñ AI Agent ‚Äì For analyzing project scope and building proposals.

üóÇÔ∏è Asana ‚Äì Project creation and task assignment.

üí¨ Slack ‚Äì For automated client channel creation and internal communication.

üìß Gmail ‚Äì For onboarding and proposal emails.

üíº HubSpot ‚Äì CRM contact creation and project linkage.

üìä Google Sheets ‚Äì For logging all onboarding and AI results.

## Optional Enhancements

üìÑ PDF Generation (PDF Munk) ‚Äì Convert AI-generated proposals into downloadable PDFs.

üí¨ Slack Interactive Approvals ‚Äì Add buttons for internal review before client communication.

üìà Performance Dashboard ‚Äì Connect Google Sheets data to Looker Studio for tracking onboarding times.

üåç Multilingual Support ‚Äì Add translation nodes for international clients.

üîê File Attachments ‚Äì Send proposal PDFs or onboarding kits automatically via Gmail.

## Quick Start

1Ô∏è‚É£ Import Template ‚Äì Copy and import the JSON file into your n8n workspace.
2Ô∏è‚É£ Set Up Jotform ‚Äì Create a form with fields for client name, company, project name, budget, and requirements.
3Ô∏è‚É£ Add Credentials ‚Äì Connect Jotform, AI Agent, Asana, Slack, Gmail, HubSpot, and Google Sheets.
4Ô∏è‚É£ Configure Sheet ID ‚Äì Replace YOUR_SHEET_ID in the Google Sheets node.
5Ô∏è‚É£ Customize Proposal HTML ‚Äì Edit AI prompt and branding to reflect your company‚Äôs style.
6Ô∏è‚É£ Test Workflow ‚Äì Submit a test form and verify Slack, Asana, Gmail, and Sheets outputs.
7Ô∏è‚É£ Deploy ‚Äì Activate workflow and share the Jotform link with your sales or operations team.

## Customization Options

1Ô∏è‚É£ Proposal Branding ‚Äì Customize proposal HTML with logos, brand colors, and formatting.
2Ô∏è‚É£ AI Prompt Tuning ‚Äì Refine the LangChain AI prompt to match your tone or project style.
3Ô∏è‚É£ Task Templates ‚Äì Adjust task names, assignees, and due dates in the Asana creation node.
4Ô∏è‚É£ Slack Messaging ‚Äì Update welcome message formatting and team introduction details.
5Ô∏è‚É£ CRM Fields ‚Äì Map additional HubSpot properties for better data tracking.
6Ô∏è‚É£ Sheet Logging ‚Äì Add more columns for tracking team recommendations or proposal scores.

## Expected Results

‚ö° 90% Faster Onboarding ‚Äì Reduce manual setup from hours to minutes.

ü§ñ AI Precision ‚Äì Intelligent proposals and team allocations that impress clients instantly.

üìà Zero Missed Steps ‚Äì Every project automatically created, communicated, and logged.

üí¨ Seamless Collaboration ‚Äì Slack, Gmail, and Asana in perfect sync.

üóÇÔ∏è Complete Transparency ‚Äì Every onboarding step logged for accountability and improvement.

üèÜ Use Cases

üßë‚Äçüíº Marketing & Creative Agencies ‚Äì Automate creative project scoping and proposal creation.

üíª Software Development Teams ‚Äì Rapidly assess client tech requirements and allocate developers.

üßæ Consulting Firms ‚Äì Build data-backed, AI-enhanced proposals for client engagements.

üè¢ Corporate PMOs ‚Äì Standardize project setup and approvals across multiple departments.

## Pro Tips

üí° Refine AI Prompt ‚Äì Include examples of past projects to improve proposal quality.

üí¨ Add Slack Approvals ‚Äì Insert ‚Äúmanager approval‚Äù logic before sending proposals.

üìÑ Attach PDFs ‚Äì Use PDF Munk for branded, downloadable proposals.

üìä Track Conversion ‚Äì Link HubSpot deal stage changes based on Asana progress.

üìÖ Monitor Efficiency ‚Äì Use Sheet timestamps to calculate average onboarding time.

## Learning Resources

parameters.jsCode:
// Generate personalized proposal content const data = $input.first().json; const proposalContent = `

Project Proposal

For ${data.companyName}

Project Overview

Project Name: ${data.projectName}

Client: ${data.clientName}

Project Type: ${data.projectType}

Timeline: ${data.timeline}

Start Date: ${data.startDate}

End Date: ${data.endDate}

Project Scope

${data.projectScope}

Recommended Team

Team Size: ${data.teamSize} professionals

Estimated Hours: ${data.estimatedHours} hours

${data.suggestedTeam.map(role => `
${role}
`).join('')}

Investment

$${data.budget.toLocaleString()}

Estimated Hourly Rate: $${data.hourlyRate}

Project Deliverables

Phase Deliverable Timeline
Phase 1: Discovery Requirements Document, Wireframes Week 1-2
Phase 2: Design Visual Designs, Prototypes Week 3-4
Phase 3: Development Working Software/Assets Week 5-10
Phase 4: Testing & Launch QA Report, Final Delivery Week 11-12

Next Steps

  1. Review and sign this proposal
  2. Complete contract via DocuSign
  3. Attend kickoff meeting
  4. Provide initial assets and access
  5. Project begins on ${data.startDate}

Thank you for choosing our agency!

Questions? Contact us at user@example.com

`; return { json: { ...data, proposalHtml: proposalContent, proposalFileName: `Proposal_${data.companyName.replace(/\s/g, '_')}_${Date.now()}.pdf` } };

üì© **TRIGGER: New Client Submission**

Captures comprehensive client details from Jotform:
‚Ä¢ Client/Company information
‚Ä¢ Project scope and requirements
‚Ä¢ Budget and timeline
‚Ä¢ Communication preferences

Create your intake form on [Jotform](https://www.jotform.com/?partner=mediajade)

**Required Form Fields:**
- Client Name
- Company Name
- Email & Phone
- Project Name & Type
- Budget & Timeline
- Project Scope (long text)
- Industry & Preferences

üßæ **PARSE & NORMALIZE**

Extracts and standardizes all client data from Jotform submission.

Handles multiple field name formats (q3_field, field, etc.)

Prepares clean data structure for downstream processing.

ü§ñ **AI AGENT - TEAM SUGGESTION**

Replaces the static logic node with a LangChain AI Agent:
‚Ä¢ Analyzes project input data
‚Ä¢ Suggests optimal roles & hours
‚Ä¢ Evaluates budget adequacy & priority
‚Ä¢ Generates justification text

üìÑ **PROPOSAL GENERATION**

Creates beautiful, branded HTML proposal:

‚Ä¢ Project overview
‚Ä¢ Recommended team
‚Ä¢ Investment breakdown
‚Ä¢ Deliverables timeline
‚Ä¢ Next steps

Ready for PDF conversion or DocuSign!

**Customize:**
Edit HTML template with your branding, colors, and logo.

üìä **PROJECT MANAGEMENT SETUP**

**Asana Project Creation:**
‚Ä¢ Creates new project
‚Ä¢ Sets timeline and notes
‚Ä¢ Links to client data

**Task Generation:**
‚Ä¢ 13 standard tasks
‚Ä¢ Auto-assigned to roles
‚Ä¢ Due dates calculated from start date
‚Ä¢ Customizable per project type

Phases: Discovery ‚Üí Design ‚Üí Development ‚Üí Testing ‚Üí Launch

üí¨ **SLACK WORKSPACE SETUP**

**Channel Creation:**
‚Ä¢ Private client-specific channel
‚Ä¢ Named: client-company-name
‚Ä¢ Topic set to project name

**Welcome Message:**
‚Ä¢ Project overview
‚Ä¢ Team introduction
‚Ä¢ Budget & timeline
‚Ä¢ Communication guidelines

**Team Invitations:**
Manually invite suggested team members or automate with Slack API!

‚úâÔ∏è **CLIENT COMMUNICATION**

**Welcome Email includes:**
‚úÖ Personalized greeting
‚úÖ Project details recap
‚úÖ Team introduction
‚úÖ Next steps checklist
‚úÖ Portal access info
‚úÖ Slack channel invite
‚úÖ Contact information

**Attachments:**
‚Ä¢ Proposal PDF

‚Ä¢ Brand Guidelines

Fully customizable HTML template!

**HubSpot Contact:**
‚Ä¢ Creates new contact
